---
title: Salmon, Creamy Zucchini & Tomato Orzotto with Toasted Panko & Lemony Arugula Salad
description: What’s orzotto? Glad you asked! You’ll cook rice-shaped orzo pasta like risotto by adding liquid to a pan and stirring over heat. Stir savory roasted zucchini and grape tomatoes into that creamy, comforting orzotto, shower with buttery toasted panko breadcrumbs and serve with a crisp arugula and almond salad and squeeze of fresh lemon juice for a bright finish.
